            "text": "1Chronicles 27:24",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". In this case the Divine wrath (",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Numbers 1:53",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ") manifested itself in a Syrian invasion (",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2Chronicles 24:23",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
