          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ")",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": ".",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Upon Judah and Jerusalem.—The sin of the nobles, allowed and perhaps imitated by the king, involved the nation in its penal consequences (Comp. 1 Chronicles 21)",
        "children": [
